*[[File:en/Manual/Base Set/Trains/Millenniumz1.png|'Millennium Z1']] [[nl/Manual/Base Set/Trains/Millennium Z1|'Millennium Z1']]
En één trein in speelgoedland landschap:
*[[File:en/Manual/Base Set/Trains/Wizzowowz99.png|Wizzowow Z99]] [[nl/Manual/Base Set/Trains/Wizzowow Z99|Wizzowow Z99]]

